---
---
<section id="desafios" class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-b from-[#0B152A] via-[#050C1B] to-cosmos-dark border-t border-gray-800">
  <!-- Subtle star overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-stars opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
  
  <!-- Backlight Glows to enhance the blue theme -->
  <div class="absolute left-1/4 top-1/4 w-[350px] h-[350px] rounded-full bg-blue-900/15 blur-[120px] pointer-events-none -z-10"></div>
  <div class="absolute right-1/4 bottom-1/4 w-[350px] h-[350px] rounded-full bg-indigo-900/10 blur-[120px] pointer-events-none -z-10"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    
    <!-- 2-Column Grid Layout: Left Title, Right Cards -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-20">
      
      <!-- Left Column: Title & Subtitle -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-4 flex flex-col justify-center text-center lg:text-left animate-on-scroll">
        <h2 class="text-gold-deep text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-4 text-glow font-sans">
          Problemas que resolvemos
        </h2>
        <h3 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-normal font-heading text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          ¿Tu empresa enfrenta alguno de estos <span class="italic text-gold-bright">desafíos</span>?
        </h3>
        <div class="w-16 h-px bg-[#3B82F6]/50 mb-8 mx-auto lg:mx-0 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(59,130,246,0.8)]"></div>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm sm:text-base font-light leading-relaxed hidden lg:block">
          Identificar y resolver estos cuellos de botella operativos es el primer paso hacia una gestión inteligente, eficiente y rentable.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: 3x2 Grid of Cards -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-8 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5" id="desafios-grid">
        
        <!-- Challenge 1: Excel -->
        <div class="glass-card p-6 flex flex-col justify-start rounded-xl border border-gray-800 relative group transition-all duration-300 hover:border-[#3B82F6]/30">
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 inset-x-0 h-12 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#3B82F6]/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
          
          <!-- Icon -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#60A5FA] mb-4 group-hover:text-gold-bright transition-colors" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/>
            <line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/>
            <line x1="3" y1="15" x2="21" y2="15"/>
            <line x1="9" y1="9" x2="9" y2="21"/>
            <line x1="15" y1="9" x2="15" y2="21"/>
            <path d="M6 5h2v2H6z" fill="currentColor" fill-opacity="0.3" stroke="none"/>
          </svg>
          
          <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2 text-glow">Excel Disperso</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs sm:text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">
            Información dispersa en múltiples archivos Excel que dificulta la consolidación.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Challenge 2: Manual Processes -->
        <div class="glass-card p-6 flex flex-col justify-start rounded-xl border border-gray-800 relative group transition-all duration-300 hover:border-[#3B82F6]/30">
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 inset-x-0 h-12 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#3B82F6]/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
          
          <!-- Icon -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#60A5FA] mb-4 group-hover:text-gold-bright transition-colors" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
            <path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/>
            <path d="M19 12a7 7 0 0 1-7 7" stroke-dasharray="2 2"/>
          </svg>
          
          <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2 text-glow">Procesos Manuales</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs sm:text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">
            Tareas repetitivas y operativas que consumen tiempo valioso del equipo.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Challenge 3: Lack of Indicators -->
        <div class="glass-card p-6 flex flex-col justify-start rounded-xl border border-gray-800 relative group transition-all duration-300 hover:border-[#3B82F6]/30">
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 inset-x-0 h-12 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#3B82F6]/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
          
          <!-- Icon -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#60A5FA] mb-4 group-hover:text-gold-bright transition-colors" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M3 3v18h18"/>
            <path d="M18.7 8l-5.1 5.2-2.8-2.7L7 14.3" stroke-dasharray="1 1"/>
            <circle cx="18.7" cy="8" r="2" fill="currentColor" fill-opacity="0.2" stroke="none"/>
          </svg>
          
          <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2 text-glow">Sin Indicadores</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs sm:text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">
            Falta de indicadores clave y KPIs en tiempo real para tomar decisiones fiables.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Challenge 4: Inventory Control -->
        <div class="glass-card p-6 flex flex-col justify-start rounded-xl border border-gray-800 relative group transition-all duration-300 hover:border-[#3B82F6]/30">
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 inset-x-0 h-12 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#3B82F6]/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
          
          <!-- Icon -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#60A5FA] mb-4 group-hover:text-gold-bright transition-colors" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 2L3 7l9 5 9-5-9-5z"/>
            <path d="M3 7v10l9 5M21 7v10l-9 5"/>
            <path d="M12 12v10"/>
          </svg>
          
          <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2 text-glow">Control de Stock</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs sm:text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">
            Dificultad constante para controlar ventas, inventarios y movimientos.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Challenge 5: Integration -->
        <div class="glass-card p-6 flex flex-col justify-start rounded-xl border border-gray-800 relative group transition-all duration-300 hover:border-[#3B82F6]/30">
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 inset-x-0 h-12 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#3B82F6]/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
          
          <!-- Icon -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#60A5FA] mb-4 group-hover:text-gold-bright transition-colors" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <circle cx="6" cy="6" r="3"/>
            <circle cx="18" cy="6" r="3"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="18" r="3"/>
            <line x1="9" y1="6" x2="15" y2="6" stroke-dasharray="2 2"/>
            <line x1="7.5" y1="8.5" x2="10.5" y2="15.5" stroke-dasharray="2 2"/>
          </svg>
          
          <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2 text-glow">Áreas Aisladas</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs sm:text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">
            Escasa integración entre departamentos, provocando islas de información.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Challenge 6: Visibility -->
        <div class="glass-card p-6 flex flex-col justify-start rounded-xl border border-gray-800 relative group transition-all duration-300 hover:border-[#3B82F6]/30">
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 inset-x-0 h-12 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#3B82F6]/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
          
          <!-- Icon -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#60A5FA] mb-4 group-hover:text-gold-bright transition-colors" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M2 12s3-7 10-7 10 7 10 7-3 7-10 7-10-7-10-7z"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/>
          </svg>
          
          <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2 text-glow">Poca Visibilidad</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs sm:text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">
            Falta de claridad sobre el desempeño general y rentabilidad del negocio.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <div class="animate-on-scroll glass-card p-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto border-t-2 border-[#3B82F6] text-center relative shadow-[0_0_35px_rgba(59,130,246,0.15)] rounded-xl">
      <div class="absolute top-0 inset-x-0 h-[2px] bg-[#3B82F6] shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(59,130,246,0.8)]"></div>
      
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white font-montserrat font-normal tracking-wide mb-8 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Pegasus Nexus convierte estos desafíos en <span class="italic text-gold-bright font-semibold text-glow">procesos digitales inteligentes</span>.
      </p>
      
      <a href="https://wa.me/59179786916?text=Hola%20Pegasus%20Nexus!%20Me%20gustar%C3%ADa%20solicitar%20un%20diagn%C3%B3stico%20para%20mi%20empresa%20y%20conocer%20c%C3%B3mo%20resolver%20nuestros%20desaf%C3%ADos." target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block bg-[#3B82F6] hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-4 px-10 rounded-lg transition-all text-xs tracking-widest uppercase shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(59,130,246,0.3)] hover:scale-105 transform cursor-pointer border border-[#3B82F6]/50">
        Solicitar Diagnóstico Gratuito
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
